reviewText: They sell this dvd at dollar tree where everything is one dollar . Plus the have several more from this collection

I enjoyed using this dvd. It is 15 minutes for each day of the week or you can play all of them.  It is not high intensity, I use this dvd on my day off from exercise because it has some really good stretches that make me feel so good.  I usually like high intensity exercises but not every day.  I do take a day or two off from exercise and do stretches and this is a good dvd for your day off.
